cdata.name: BHPCash
cdata.desc:
Bank of Hash Power (BHP) is ablockchain financial management platform derived from the global hash power asset. Users are able to access a set of financial tools to manage their digital assets. Bank of Hash Powerworks as a decentralized bank system that uses the Bitcoin hash power as a collateral.

The BHPCash (BHPC) token is an Ethereum-based (ERC-20) cryptocurrency. It is issued by BHP and its acceptance of credit endorsement is the hash power of Bitcoin, Ethereum and other mainstream digital currency.
